Fundsupermart.com Hong Kong (FSM HK) is the one-stop online investment platform and the retail division of iFAST Financial (HK) Limited.

With our mission statement, “To help investors around the world invest globally and profitably”, we provide a wide range of investment products including Funds, Bonds, ETFs, Stocks and Managed Portfolios, supported by user-friendly website and mobile application, in-house research content and responsive customer service support.

We believe in creating a corporate environment which is highly open and receptive in nature. At FSM HK, we give our employees sufficient opportunities to shine and excel in their area of work.

To find out more about FSM HK, please visit: http://www.fundsupermart.com.hk/

You may also refer to the corporate website for our corporate information and services: http://www.ifastcorp.com/

You are welcome to directly contact HR team on LinkedIn.


Analyze and research on mutual funds, portfolios, markets and other investment products;

Write original and timely articles on equity markets, mutual funds and investment-related products;

Involved in presenting to clients and financial advisors;

To contribute to senior member on materials and data preparation;

To support the research team to maintain database/research content & tools/portfolio monitoring.


A good degree in Economic/ Finance/ Mathematics or related discipline, fresh graduates are welcomed to apply;

Advanced knowledge in mutual fund and macro-economic analysis is preferred;

Excellent writing and presentation skills in both English and Chinese;

Keen interest in investments, financial markets and economics;

Meticulous, precise and sensitive to numbers;

Strong analytical ability with good communication and interpersonal skills;

Sense of urgency;

Self-motivated, mature and able to work independently as well as be a team player.


Career development prospect;

Attractive remuneration;

5-day working week;

21+ days Annual Leave;

Medical, Dental, Life Insurance;

Performance bonus and shares;

Education, sports allowance.

Our company is an equal opportunities employer and welcome application from all qualified candidates. Information provided will be treated with strict confidential and be used for the purpose of selection only. Applicants who are not invited for interview within 10 weeks may consider their applications unsuccessful. Personal data of unsuccessful applicant will be destroyed within 12 months.

Full-time,Permanent

